 The secondary one, the yellow, activates the red lights in the underground room, that at the beggining are blackedout, this one can be use infinite times...

Its a closed map, and it has varius tunnels, and it doesen't have a buy zone, but numerous weapons, some hidden, scatterd all around.

This is the final version for the map Ishar 2. Inspired in one abandonaware game called Ishar 2: Messenger of Doom. This map works only with GarrysMod and CSS. This map is a test that mixed Irvan's Island and Zach's Island in one small map. The target is to do finally those islands individually. This is the final version, as there is another one in garrysmod.org with the same name that is alpha. Extract in : C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\user\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps

_sText: This is a revamp of the original. You start on the top this time. Every unit is filled with glass. The grenades are no longer present. Oh and there's a deadly pit. Now please, actually play the map before rating it. And I may have worked on it for an hour, but come on! So was fy_iceworld, and see how popular that is?

_sText: This is a map I made in less than an hour. It is a huge room with many floors of glass. There are four additional glass walls going around all floors one unit in. Ladders in all 4 corners bring you up to the higher floors. On the top floor there are grenades in the center. I now realize that it would've been a better idea to have the spawn points on the top floor. Oh well.

This is the Irvan's Island as you can see in the game Ishar 2 Messenger of Doom, Plus include the nav file for bots. This pretend to be a recreation of this island from the ms-dos graphics to source engine. Works also for Gmod. Extract in : C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\user\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps

A simple map for Invisible Man.
Map by The_Prodigy

A simple map for Invisible Man. Map by The_Prodigy

1. There is a minimap

2. Present env_cubemap (to reflect the world in the models and textures by)

3. Map voiced

4. Used func_occluder, hint, skip to optimize the map.

5. Map of Escape. After 3 minutes, the boat sails.

6. There is a small bonus, each surviving person is given 10 frags. I think it's not very much, because very rarely survive people, not kill invisible.

7. There is a break areas

This map is intended for aim practice (obviously) and there isn't many features in the map, but more will be added as time goes by.

More Information

To go to your paper to see how you've done, there are two small doors - one on the left and another on the right.


To buy weapons, simply go up to the counter or whatever you want to call it and it will trigger a buy zone.


Before starting the game, in the "Create Game" menu, you should set your buytime to a high amount because there is no possible way for you to get any money in this level.


Type "sv_cheats 1" and then "impulse 101" to get full money for more weapons. If you run out of money again just type in "impulse 101" without typing "sv_cheats 1"
